messages.message:
@Serena, @Vishnu - Is there a ticket or something to track for being able to create more attributes for a list field? Also would / could this be different between MT and ST environments?

This is currently being raised by SwissRe in their use of AI Hub (cc: @Jasper, @Matthias Bauer).

For the short term I would collect multiple lists.  Nationwide has bordereau documents with 90 columns where we will need to collect 9 or more lists.  I state or more as the unique key for each row will have to be duplicated.
there is currently no ticket for creating more attributes for a list field, feel free to create one!
Why any limit at all?  Customers should be given the power and the option to learn when their documents begin to loose accuracy
Its a good point, its good for us to have a warning at least to give guidance to end users
updated the name of the ticket
Agree with providing guidance to educate the user!
